Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:40.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96784,100121}How about going to buy chocolate\Nafter school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100330,102624}It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102790,106544}I'll have to give some\Nobligation chocolates this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:51.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106753,111299}-Meimi, you're going too, right?\N-Valentine's. What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111507,114302}Aren't you giving\NAsuka Jr. chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114552,116179}What? You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116387,119223}What's that?\NIs that how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:03.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119432,123811}Someone's giving me chocolate?\N"True love" chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124020,127815}You've got it wrong!\NIt's obligation chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128024,129776}I don't care which it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129984,134280}…but a better gift would be\Na meat bun or octopus fritters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134489,138618}What a kid! Valentine chocolates\Naren't a 3:00 snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138826,141663}You won't get any\N"true love" chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141871,144832}-Be quiet!\N-What do you mean, be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145041,147585}-What's it to you?\N-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147794,149629}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150213,153466}Asuka, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:38.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153966,158429}That's no way to treat a lady.\NYou've got to be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160181,162392}It's Tohru Ijuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162850,165603}Hey, who's Tohru Ijuin\Nsupposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165812,169691}You don't know?\NRight now, Tohru Ijuin is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170233,173194}…an ultra-popular guy\Namong the freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173444,177240}Sure! He models, always\Nin the latest magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177448,180743}Then how could such a guy\Nknow Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180952,182662}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183287,186499}Oh, good morning!\NI'm a freshmen in class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187083,189168}Tohru Ijuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192880,198094}THE HEART THIEF ON\NST. VALENTINE'S DAY??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:27.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201681,207353}Just know that I'm not friends with\Nthis guy. We live near each other--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:31.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207562,211357}That's mean!\NWe played a lot together as children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211566,213901}Be quiet, don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:39.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214110,219449}In the first place, you're younger!\NSo why are you bigger than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219782,223119}Asuka, you're at it again?\NHe's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223327,226998}He absolutely despises my good looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230710,235131}-Pardon me! You're Tohru Ijuin, right?\N-Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:59.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235339,239177}-Isn't she from another school?\N-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239385,243514}-Please enjoy these cookies I made.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243723,246684}And will you let me take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246893,249020}-Sure.\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249270,255109}Wait a minute! I look best diagonally\Nfrom the right, at a 30-degree angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255318,258738}Okay! I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:23.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258946,263326}This is stupid.\NLet's go and leave this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267079,270208}Hey, wait for me, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270750,274420}Asuka! Please wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274629,276214}Yeah, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276631,281469}"There is nothing stronger\Nthan a mother's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281677,285264}I am prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:50.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285598,290603}The mountain that you see\Nover there is Mt. Asahi."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291229,293356}Well, we shall stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:58.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293564,298528}We will have a test next week\Non today's lesson. Review it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298778,302573}-What?\N-You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312375,316963}Can you lend me your English notebook?\NI didn't take any notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317213,318464}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318673,322176}Hey, Tohru! Hurry up\Nor I'll leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322385,325721}Yeah. Give me a minute!\NIs it no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326430,328474}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332562,334730}Here, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:38.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335189,338276}Thank you!\NI'll return it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:46.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342655,346826}This is the English notebook.\NWait! That's the wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349787,353291}Oh, no, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355501,359547}-What? You're gonna buy that much?\N-But they're all obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359755,362133}And who's the true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:06.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362341,366262}That's a secret!\NAnd, Meimi, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366470,367930}What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372476,375980}-Who'd give him anything?\N-Meimi, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376188,378399}That's my secret too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378608,381110}Unfair, you've all got secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381319,384280}-So, Ryoko, yours is…?\N-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:28.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384488,388367}You keep asking about us,\Nbut what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388576,391954}Isn't it obvious? It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392163,393456}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393664,395166}A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401047,403883}So you lent him the wrong notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404175,406135}Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406344,410222}That notebook is the one\NI use as a diary…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410431,412850}…to write my daily thoughts in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:59.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415227,419357}In that notebook,\NI've written many poems…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419565,422151}…thinking about Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423235,426614}If Tohru should see any of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:12.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426822,432078}…I'd be so embarrassed\NI wouldn't be able to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:17.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432536,437541}Don't worry.\NI'm sure God will lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446258,449011}Get a notebook back from Tohru Ijuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449553,451889}Right. And it has to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,455977}Before he gets a chance\Nto look at that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456185,457728}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457937,462108}Kanako Shimamura is in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462316,465444}But she's afraid\Nto have him find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:50.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465653,470950}This would be the chance to tell him.\NAnd it's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471200,474870}You may be right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:08:01.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475079,481168}A boy as popular as Tohru would\Nnever even give me a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:05.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481377,485798}And I'm happy just to\Nbe able to look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:11.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486507,491595}There are many girls who are unable\Nto honestly display their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491804,494223}Meimi, you're probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496100,497393}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:22.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497810,502106}I understand. Right!\NSt. Tail is a supporter of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502314,505609}I will get that notebook\Nback for Kanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505818,507611}ART ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513200,516912}-Let's clean up quickly and go home!\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519040,522334}Jeez, what a filthy classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527673,529425}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533095,536849}"NOTE" GETS CHANGED\NTO "HEART"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537058,538517}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538726,540352}It's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541437,545399}Tonight I will be stealing\NTohru Ijuin's heart away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545608,547860}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549153,551405}His heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551614,553741}What about his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:19.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553949,559497}-What are you doing here?\N-Let's go home together, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559705,562291}Never mind that. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563125,568297}"Tonight I will be stealing\NTohru Ijuin's heart away. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568881,571801}-What's this about?\N-That's my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574095,575846}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:40.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576055,580017}If it says "heart"…\NYou're kidding! My heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:45.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580267,585648}This heart? She's gonna perform\Nopen-heart surgery on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585856,589902}Of course not, you idiot!\NThink seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:54.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590152,594240}For example, maybe you have\Na pet cat or dog named Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594448,597701}-No, only a turtle named Samantha.\N-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598160,600538}Then what could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600704,604166}What could St. Tail\Nwant to steal from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605167,606710}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609672,612424}Heart, heart, heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612633,615636}That's it!\NI know what it is, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615886,619515}What is it? What's she gonna steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619723,621350}To put it simply…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621559,625813}…St. Tail has fallen in love\Nwith me, and tonight she's coming…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626021,629608}…to flirt with me\Nand steal my heart away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629817,632778}-Think seriously!\N-I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632987,636866}Besides, what else could\N"steal my heart away" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637074,640077}Stupid. That's just stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640494,643789}Asuka, what are you so upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:48.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644039,648627}Asuka! Could you be jealous\Nof how I attract all the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648836,650296}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650504,653674}That St. Tail, with a guy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653883,656343}I, Tohru Ijuin…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:00.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656594,660055}…shall allow my heart to be stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663058,665477}-What's wrong?\N-Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682745,684830}Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685623,688083}Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688250,690669}Where else? To buy a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690878,694340}We're going to buy a present\Nto give St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:38.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694506,698010}A present? Look here!\NWhat are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:43.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698677,703265}St. Tail is coming to steal\Nmy heart away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:47.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703474,707019}Wouldn't it be rude\Nnot to be prepared for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707228,709730}Imbecile! She's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:54.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709939,714026}Never mind. Just tell me\Nwhat gift would make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714235,716528}How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:04.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719531,724036}Okay, I can't be\Ndragging my feet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732336,734380}That wonderful chocolate smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:19.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734588,739510}-Don't look yet.\N-Why? What's wrong with it? Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:24.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739760,744056}I said no. I haven't put\Nthe finishing touch on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744265,746558}The finishing touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747726,750062}A special flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750938,753983}With lots of love! Sprinkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754191,756443}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757569,760489}You're right. This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:44.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760698,764451}-Isn't it?\N-I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:50.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766120,770457}Listening to them is embarrassing.\NIsn't that so, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773335,776505}Aren't I right? Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776714,780968}Ruby, do you have someone\Nto give chocolates to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:20.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796233,800154}I've been waiting for you.\NWell? Don't I look great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800821,803657}Hey, what are you up to, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803866,806076}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:30.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806285,810581}This is the proper etiquette\Nfor receiving a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811874,816420}Kanako, it's dinnertime!\NCome down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816628,819590}Yes! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824845,828557}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833562,834563}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837149,838692}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840277,842654}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856418,859505}Please be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859880,862049}Yes, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864343,867971}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:37.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873727,877314}You can stay,\Nbut please don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877523,879983}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880734,884279}St. Tail, come if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884488,886990}I'll get you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887199,890369}Who would give St. Tail\Nto a creep like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890577,892746}My style!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893747,895499}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895707,896917}Wait, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897751,899753}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902256,904675}What's the matter, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905300,909430}It's a present, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910097,913851}Wait a minute, idiot!\NDon't bring that in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914435,916520}But why--?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917980,922067}What did I tell you?! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925821,927781}It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930284,932494}Quick! Open the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934455,936498}Is that you, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:41.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937249,941170}-This must be it.\N-St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941420,944756}Please steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946300,950262}-Why are you running away?\N-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950471,953265}Where are you?\NWhere did you go, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953765,955726}Please steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955934,958187}What? Steal his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959605,961857}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962524,966945}Stop it! I'm not St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967779,969698}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970949,972784}Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973911,975913}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977581,980792}Do you love Tohru that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981293,984421}What's he mixed-up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984838,987758}I'm taking the notebook,\Njust as I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988300,990260}Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:40.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994848,1000187}Oh, it's not "heart."\NIt's "notebook."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000604,1004233}-See you around!\N-I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004441,1006276}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014201,1015786}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016703,1018789}Steal my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028215,1031260}-You're in the way!\N-No, you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031468,1034388}I'm gonna catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034846,1037224}Asuka, up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043397,1048068}My heart, please steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:36.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052030,1056326}I'm pretty sure that\NKanako's house is in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060372,1062499}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:47.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064084,1067170}Please wait! My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068171,1070632}Something's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070841,1074094}-St. Tail!\N-I'll go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085897,1088317}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088734,1090819}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101580,1103457}I give you my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103665,1105584}Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112215,1114051}You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116928,1119056}I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124895,1125979}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130275,1132903}Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137866,1140369}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146124,1148418}Now you're caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149127,1151129}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157302,1159930}I'll remember this, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160138,1163934}You won't get away from me next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:45.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180659,1185789}What happened to you yesterday?\NYou said you'd buy chocolate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:50.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186039,1190168}Oh, sorry about that!\NSomething urgent came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190961,1195006}Good morning, Asuka Jr.!\NSt. Tail got away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195257,1198885}Be quiet! I almost had her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:04.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199094,1204349}If only that ship hadn't passed!\NNext time, I'll get her for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204558,1208979}Asuka! Asuka, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209855,1212274}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212733,1215152}-Kanako?\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:19.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215360,1219322}-Where are your glasses?\N-I changed to contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219531,1222993}She's much cuter this way, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224327,1227205}Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227414,1230751}My heart was stolen,\Njust like the notice said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230959,1232335}By St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232544,1235046}Of course not! By Kanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235255,1237257}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237466,1241595}You better hurry too,\Nor you'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242387,1243847}-But…\N-Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244055,1245599}What a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245807,1249644}We're the happiest people alive!
